OL,3,CEngland fans expecting comfortable win
OL,4,Cas flights booked for knockouts
OL,6,FConfident England fans have booked non-
OL,7,Frefundable flights for the knockout
OL,8,Fstages ahead of their final World Cup
OL,9,Fgroup game ` with one saying "you
OL,10,Fcould get a team from Brooklyn that
OL,11,Fwould beat Panama".
OL,13,FMore than 15,000 Three Lions
OL,14,Fsupporters are expected to travel to
OL,15,FNew Jersey for the game on Saturday,
OL,16,Fwith many taking the opportunity to
OL,17,Fcombine the trip with a sightseeing
OL,18,Ftour of nearby New York City.
OL,26,@qD@^OUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
