OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland fans expecting comfortable win
OL,4,Cas flights booked for knockouts
OL,6,FBack in the UK, the late kick-off time
OL,7,Fof 10pm is expected to spare
OL,8,Fsupporters from the daytime
OL,9,Ftemperatures of more than 30Cs in east
OL,10,Fand south east England, as many are
OL,11,Fset to flock to pubs to watch the
OL,12,Fmatch.
OL,14,FOn Friday, fans in New York said they
OL,15,Fbelieved Panama, who are at number 42
OL,16,Fin the Fifa rankings, would be no
OL,17,Fmatch for England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland fans expecting comfortable win
OL,4,Cas flights booked for knockouts
OL,6,FPeter Harding, 74, from the north east
OL,7,Ftown of Whitley Bay, told the Press
OL,8,FAssociation: "You could get a team
OL,9,Ffrom Brooklyn that would beat Panama.
OL,11,F"A team from Whitley Bay would give
OL,12,FPanama a good game."
OL,14,FAnother supporter said he booked a non-
OL,15,Frefundable flight to Atlanta, where
OL,16,FEngland will play should they top
OL,17,Ftheir group.
OL,19,FRichie Slaughter, 35, from Hexham in
OL,20,FNorthumberland, said: "I think we've
OL,21,Fgot a good chance tomorrow.
OL,26,@pD@NOUsD@AOUtD@TO]|D@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland fans expecting comfortable win
OL,4,Cas flights booked for knockouts
OL,6,F"Hopefully we beat them anyway ` we've
OL,7,Falready booked the flights to Atlanta
OL,8,Fand a non-refundable one, so praying
OL,9,Fthey'll get the win tomorrow.
OL,11,F"I don't know why, but we booked them
OL,12,Fthe morning of the Ghana game, and
OL,13,Fthen that obviously didn't go to
OL,14,Fplan... but I'm still positive we'll
OL,15,Fbe there."
OL,17,FDespite sharing Mr Slaughter's
OL,18,Fconfidence, other fans were more
OL,19,Fhesitant on planning for the knockout
OL,20,Fstages.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
