OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782638299
OL,3,CEngland fans expecting comfortable win
OL,4,Cas flights booked for knockouts
OL,6,FAnother supporter getting the train,
OL,7,FBlackpool fan Tom Wilson, 32, who now
OL,8,Flives in Buckinghamshire, said:
OL,9,F"Whilst I think it's very expensive,
OL,10,Fit looks like the best option given
OL,11,Fsome of the videos I've seen on the
OL,12,Finternet of traffic etc.
OL,14,F"I hate to say it's worth it, given
OL,15,Fthat, but it seems to be so."
